title.narrative: PROCOFSERVICES and P0053 for West Bengal : Kolkata Urban Services for the Poor

description.narrative: This activity (PROCOFSERVICES and P0053 for West Bengal : Kolkata Urban Services for the Poor) is a component of West Bengal : Kolkata Urban Services for the Poor reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £8,549,995. This component benefits India, and works in the following sector(s): Public sector policy and administrative management, Public finance management (PFM), Decentralisation and support to subnational government. , with the following implementing partners: British Council, Deloitte Touche Tohmatsu India LLP, Ernst & Young, ICF Consulting Services Ltd, IPE Global Private Limited, PwC India. The start date is 01-04-2003 and the end date is 31-12-2015.
